#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.metrics.r2_score.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.learn.metrics.r2\\_score"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._regression.r2_score:1 of
msgid ":math:`R^2` (coefficient of determination) regression score function."
msgstr ":math:`R^2`（决定系数）回归评分函数。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._regression.r2_score:3 of
msgid ""
"Best possible score is 1.0 and it can be negative (because the model can "
"be arbitrarily worse). A constant model that always predicts the expected"
" value of y, disregarding the input features, would get a :math:`R^2` "
"score of 0.0."
msgstr ""
"最佳可能得分为 1.0，且得分可能为负（因为模型可能表现任意差）。一个总是"
"预测 y 的期望值而忽略输入特征的常量模型将得到 :math:`R^2` 得分 0.0。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._regression.r2_score:8 of
msgid "Read more in the :ref:`User Guide <r2_score>`."
msgstr "更多信息请参见 :ref:`用户指南 <r2_score>`。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._regression.r2_score of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._regression.r2_score:10 of
msgid "Ground truth (correct) target values."
msgstr "真实（正确）的目标值。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._regression.r2_score:12 of
msgid "Estimated target values."
msgstr "估计的目标值。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._regression.r2_score:14 of
msgid "Sample weights."
msgstr "样本权重。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._regression.r2_score:16 of
msgid ""
"Defines aggregating of multiple output scores. Array-like value defines "
"weights used to average scores. Default is \"uniform_average\".  "
"'raw_values' :     Returns a full set of scores in case of multioutput "
"input.  'uniform_average' :     Scores of all outputs are averaged with "
"uniform weight.  'variance_weighted' :     Scores of all outputs are "
"averaged, weighted by the variances     of each individual output."
msgstr ""
"定义多个输出得分的聚合方式。类数组的值定义用于平均得分的权重。默认为 \""
"uniform_average\"。  'raw_values' : 在多输出输入的情况下返回完整的一组"
"得分。  'uniform_average' : 所有输出的得分以相同权重平均。  'variance_"
"weighted' : 所有输出的得分以各自输出的方差为权重进行平均。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._regression.r2_score:16 of
msgid ""
"Defines aggregating of multiple output scores. Array-like value defines "
"weights used to average scores. Default is \"uniform_average\"."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._regression.r2_score:20 of
msgid "'raw_values' :"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._regression.r2_score:21 of
msgid "Returns a full set of scores in case of multioutput input."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._regression.r2_score:23 of
msgid "'uniform_average' :"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._regression.r2_score:24 of
msgid "Scores of all outputs are averaged with uniform weight."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._regression.r2_score:26 of
msgid "'variance_weighted' :"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._regression.r2_score:27 of
msgid ""
"Scores of all outputs are averaged, weighted by the variances of each "
"individual output."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._regression.r2_score of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._regression.r2_score:31 of
msgid ""
"**z** -- The :math:`R^2` score or ndarray of scores if 'multioutput' is "
"'raw_values'."
msgstr ""
"**z** -- :math:`R^2` 得分，若 'multioutput' 为 'raw_values' 则返回得分的 "
"ndarray。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._regression.r2_score of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._regression.r2_score:36 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._regression.r2_score:37 of
msgid "This is not a symmetric function."
msgstr "这不是一个对称函数。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._regression.r2_score:39 of
msgid ""
"Unlike most other scores, :math:`R^2` score may be negative (it need not "
"actually be the square of a quantity R)."
msgstr ""
"与大多数其他得分不同，:math:`R^2` 得分可能为负（它实际上不一定是某个量 R "
"的平方）。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._regression.r2_score:42 of
msgid ""
"This metric is not well-defined for single samples and will return a NaN "
"value if n_samples is less than two."
msgstr "该指标对于单个样本未良好定义，如果 n_samples 小于 2 将返回 NaN 值。"

